om\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23121552\/menton-france-13.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-menton-is-famous-for-lemons\">Menton is famous for lemons<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Lemon growing is a huge part of Menton&#x2019;s culture. It is thought to be one of the warmest places on the coastline (with over 316 days of sunshine a year) and this unique microclimate has made it perfect for growing gorgeous lemon trees! You&#x2019;ll see them everywhere: in the parks, along the streets, and dotted over the surrounding countryside. A must-do, while you&#x2019;re on your trip to Menton, is to enjoy all the shops selling various lemon products. Whether it&#x2019;s a lemon liqueur, lemon soaps, or lemon-infused olive oil, Menton will have it!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> Visiting towards the end of Feb? Don&#x2019;t miss the legendary lemon festival held in Menton every year. (F&#xEA;te du Citron)<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15.jpg\" alt=\"menton france lemons\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"menton france lemons\" class=\"wp-image-63090 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-1440x960.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-600x400.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23122543\/menton-france-15.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>Things to do in Menton<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-stroll-around-old-town\">Stroll around Old Town&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The old town is the gem of Menton, home to stunning medieval buildings and streets that take your breath away. As you explore the maze of narrow roads, remember this part of town was founded by pirates in the 13th century! Climb the steep streets all the way to the cathedral, admiring the colored houses, the grand villas, and the elegant Baroque buildings around every corner.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/bordeaux\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The best things to do in Bordeaux, France<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084404\/menton-france-9.jpg\" alt=\"menton france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"menton france\" class=\"wp-image-63074 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084404\/menton-france-9.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084404\/menton-france-9-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\