w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125952\/menton-france-18-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125952\/menton-france-18.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125952\/menton-france-18-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125952\/menton-france-18-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-basilique-saint-michel-archange\">Basilique Saint-Michel-Archange&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At the top of the old town, discover the beauty of the Basilique Saint-Michel-Archange. This gorgeous Baroque cathedral has a stunning facade and interior, complete with a magnificent ceiling mural. The cathedral also has two towers, which are unique, a 35-meter high clock tower and a 53-meter high steeple.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/menton-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See all the hotels options in Menton.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16.jpg\" alt=\"menton france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"243\" height=\"338\" alt=\"menton france\" class=\"wp-image-63094 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1381px) 100vw, 1381px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16.jpg 1381w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-432x600.jpg 432w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-583x810.jpg 583w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-243x338.jpg 243w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-117x163.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-129x180.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-552x768.jpg 552w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-737x1024.jpg 737w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-777x1080.jpg 777w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-1036x1440.jpg 1036w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-300x417.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-600x834.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23123530\/menton-france-16-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/stat