=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23084353\/menton-france-8-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-plage-des-sablettes\">Plage des Sablettes&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Plage des Sablettes is a stunning boulevard at the edge of the old town that hugs the white sand beach. Here, you&#x2019;ll find beautiful fountains, scenic restaurants, and a buzzing atmosphere. It is known as a place to gather for young people and families, where everyone can enjoy the various amenities. There are beaches with some private parts. This will give you access to the lovely shallow water, parasols, and sunbeds, with a view of Menton&#x2019;s colorful buildings.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/sarlat-dordogne\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Complete guide to the Dordogne Valley (Sarlat)<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23125402\/menton-france-17.jpg\" alt=\"menton france french riviera\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"menton france french riviera\" class=\"wp-image-63101 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com