pg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-jean-cocteau-museum\">Jean Cocteau Museum<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Jean Cocteau was a famous artist and film director who loved Menton. In fact, it was one of his favorite places! Because of this, a museum was dedicated to him within the town, chosen by Jean himself, to display his work. Uniquely, the museum is built within the bastion, a 17th-century fort, that&#x2019;s been decorated with beautiful mosaics by Jean Cocteau. His work is really eclectic and well worth a visit on your trip to Menton!<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/62747&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23135111\/menton-france-2-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23135111\/menton-france-2-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23135111\/menton-france-2-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Menton, France: The Pearl of the French Riviera\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-day-trip-to-monaco\">Day Trip to Monaco<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Monaco is an independent state and one of the most glamorous places in the world! Hop on the train and spend the day in Monaco. Visit the grand palace, casinos that inspired the James Bond film, and wander along the harbor admiring the superyachts. Much like the rest of this coastline, the climate is spectacular and there are plenty of tropical gardens to explore. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When you&#x2019;re done soaking up the lifestyle of the rich and famous, head down to the main strip of beach for a dip in the sea and a bite to eat at one of the many upscale restaurants. Monaco is a must-see, even if just for a quick stop on your trip to Menton.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>How to get there:<\/strong> Take a train from Menton in 11 minutes.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23121602\/menton-france-14.jpg\" alt=\"monaco france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"monaco france\" class=\"wp-image-63086 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23121602\/menton-france-14.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/