19;s less crowded. It can also still be warm enough to enjoy the beach!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/menton-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See all the hotels options in Menton.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera \"><\/noscript><img width=\"248\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera \" class=\"wp-image-63113 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1406px) 100vw, 1406px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19.jpg 1406w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19-439x600.jpg 439w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19-593x810.jpg 593w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19-248x338.jpg 248w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19-119x163.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19-132x180.jpg 132w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/23131901\/menton-france-19-562x768.j